],{"id":529,"depth":302,"text":530},{"id":608,"depth":131,"text":608},"Git","2026-02-26 09:39:40","使用 git rebase 或 git commit --amend 重寫 commit 歷史後，必須強制推送才能更新遠端，但 git push --force 會無條件覆蓋遠端，可能導致同事的工作丟失。這篇文章介紹更安全的替代方案 git push --force-with-lease 與 --force-if-includes，讓你在強制推送前多一層保護。","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fgit\u002Fgit-push-force-git-push-force-with-lease","4",{"title":6,"description":733},false,"Git\u002F取代-git-push-force-更好的方式，git-push-force-with-lease",[731,743],"多人協作",null,"\u002Fgit\u002F20260226\u002F799954596\u002F","EN5-10D3C1l7-bR4xsKCfE5Mr9OZSurAJPW0j4QPzpA",{"newer":748,"older":752},{"url":749,"title":750,"date":751},"\u002Fai\u002F20260303\u002F3167917304\u002F","Gemini Gems 教學：輕鬆打造你的專屬 AI 助手","2026-03-03 16:34:17",{"url":753,"title":754,"date":755},"\u002Fother\u002F20260222\u002F1723617915\u002F","macOS 時光機備份超久？教你一招加速！","2026-02-22 11:30:22",[757,762,766],{"url":758,"title":759,"date":760,"readingMinutes":761},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260122\u002F21277993\u002F","Git init 出現 master 分支提示？教你設定預設分支為 main","2026-01-22 16:20:40","2",{"url":763,"title":764,"date":765,"readingMinutes":738},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F","Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","2026-01-21 16:04:27",{"url":767,"title":768,"date":769,"readingMinutes":770},"\u002Fgit\u002F20241220\u002F649474526\u002F","新 Git 指令之你該試試看了","2024-12-20 23:30:28","3",1784087350258]